        </div>
        <div class="question-content">
          <h5 class="answer">
            Absolutely! If you describe the website or share specific details
            about it, I can identify and replicate the layout, reverse-engineer
            its features and match its fonts and colours.
          </h5>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq">
        <div class="question-header">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
