          >
          <h5 class="question">
            What is the cost of designing and building a modern website?
          </h5>
        </div>
        <div class="question-content">
          <h5 class="answer">
            When hiring a professional to build a modern, bespoke website for
            you, you are paying for expertise and time.<br />The cost will
            depend entirely on whether you are building a simple digital
            business card or a high-performance piece of online real estate.<br
            /> A small club website might cost around $1000, whereas one with added
            functionality, like a membership signup system, might cost proportionately
            more.
          </h5>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq">
        <div class="question-header">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
