            ><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19" class="faq-btn"></line>
            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" class="faq-btn"></line></svg
          >
          <h5 class="question">
            How long does it take to complete a typical project?
          </h5>
        </div>
        <div class="question-content">
          <h5 class="answer">
            Typically, a one-page website takes 1 to 2 weeks to complete,
            although I have built some faster than that.
            <br />A website with 6 to 8 pages normally takes 4 to 6 weeks to go
            live. However, in practice, factors like the content bottleneck
            (text and photos not yet available) or custom features may extend
            the timeline.
          </h5>
        </div>
      </div>
