          >
          <h5 class="question">
            Do you offer support and maintenance after launch?
          </h5>
        </div>
        <div class="question-content">
          <h5 class="answer">
            All projects include free support and maintenance for a short period
            to fix any bugs or issues that may arise immediately after launch.<br
            />
            Following this, a support and maintenance package will be quoted for separately.
            This includes content updates, plugin updates, site backups, feature enhancements
            and performance tuning.
          </h5>
        </div>
